column8: Pickle Ceramic Jars (Set of 2)
column28:
These traditional Indian ceramic jars, referred to as a “burney” are handcrafted by a skilled potter in India to help you store your pickles, chutneys, spices and other condiments. For generations now, Indians believe that the natural material of the jar does not affect or alter the taste, flavor and color of the contents but infact enhances its nutritional value. Ceramic is a good preservative and keeps germs, bacteria and fungus away, making it ideal for storing food items for long.
  • Color: Multicolor
  • Measurements (inches): Height: 4 inches and Diameter: 3 inches
  • Material(s): Ceramic
  • Care: NA
  • Weight (GRAMS): NA
